        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". Charges against a Bride. He who, from a base motive, falsely accuses his wife of unchastity before marriage shall after solemn rebuke from the elders be fined 100 silver-pieces and have his right of divorce withdrawn (",
        "children": []
