      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " - The laws in this section have the design of fostering purity and fidelity in the relation of the sexes, and also of protecting the female against the malice of sated lust and the violence of brutal lust. (For the case supposed in ver. 13, cf. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
